{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412460/extras/title_humanity.png?t=1690042985\" /><br><strong>Mankind's Last Stand</strong> is an epic off-world 3rd-person shooter. Take command of the mighty Decimator, customize and upgrade its weapons to crush alien invaders. Prepare for intense boss fights, stock up on boosters, and reclaim all zones to restore peace and order.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>SKIN &amp; WEAPON CUSTOMIZATIONS</strong></h2>Take command of the mighty Decimator to defend humanity's space colonies from alien invader threats. Customize your tank with unique skins and weapon upgrades at the hangar.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412460/extras/gif_custom_feat.gif?t=1690042985\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>STOCK UP ON BOOSTERS</strong></h2>Are you a looter or a spender? Boosters can make or break your mission success! Gain them through looting from enemies or buy them from the Item Shop before each missions.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412460/extras/gif_item_shop.gif?t=1690042985\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>DEFEAT ENEMIES</strong></h2>Strategically swap between weapons to effectively eliminate different types of enemies. Unleash your firepower and obliterate ground and airborne invaders in your path!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412460/extras/gif_defeat_enemy.gif?t=1690042985\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>BEAT ALL BOSSES</strong></h2>Do you have what it takes to challenge the bosses in each zone and emerge victorious?<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412460/extras/gif_beat_boss.gif?t=1690042985\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>RESTORE PEACE &amp; ORDER</strong></h2>Reclaim all zones and re-establi